headline.main: Spurs Beat Timberwolves in OT, Clinch Playoff Spot
headline.print_headline: Spurs Beat Timberwolves in OT, Clinch Playoff Spot

lead_paragraph: Kawhi Leonard and the Spurs didn't get much sleep after a long night's work Friday. It didn't seem to bother San Antonio's All-Star forward, at least.
